  dialogueLines:
  - text: Why hello there, young one. Would you like a drink?
    portraitIndex: 0
    choices: []
  - text: "I know atleast one digit from a carnie and that\u2019s all I got for ya."
    portraitIndex: 0
    choices: []
  - text: One of the numbers is... Zero.
    portraitIndex: 0
    choices: []
  - text: ' Now go talk to other carnies for more info or something.'
    portraitIndex: 0
    choices: []
  - text: You want more help?
    portraitIndex: 0
    choices: []
  - text: Geez... best thing I can tell ya is sometimes you have to try again if
      you fail the first time.
    portraitIndex: 0
    choices: []
  - text: 'Now go, I''ve got a buisness to run '
    portraitIndex: 0
    choices: []
